# BRAINOID, an octave/matlab P300 Speller Library #

Brainoid is a bundle of programs developed for P300 speller Brain
Computer Interfaces (BCI).


The program is mainly composed of 3 parts:

app 	    - an Android app which can generate a flash pattern.
analyzer    - a bundle of Octave/Matlab functions for analyzing EEG data.
wrappers    - an interface to transfer sampled EEG data for analyzing.


